{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce1-043-044-hurry-up",
    "title": "Lesson 43: Hurry up!",
    "audioFilename": "043&044－Hurry Up.mp3",
    "duration": 78.864,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.46,
      "end": 2.1,
      "text": "Lesson 43.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第43课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 3.32,
      "end": 4.16,
      "text": "Hurry Up.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "快点！"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 5.94,
      "end": 9.78,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 11.44,
      "end": 16.1,
      "text": "How do you know Sam doesn't make the tea very often?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你怎么知道萨姆不常沏茶？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 18.28,
      "end": 20.62,
      "text": "Can you make the tea, Sam?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "萨姆，你会沏茶吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 22.12,
      "end": 25.16,
      "text": "Yes, of course I can, Penny.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "会，我当然会，彭妮。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 26.94,
      "end": 29.74,
      "text": "Is there any water in this kettle?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这个水壶里有水吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 30.66,
      "end": 32.48,
      "text": "Yes, there is.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "有。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 33.58,
      "end": 34.72,
      "text": "Where's the tea?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "茶叶在哪里？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 35.3,
      "end": 38.82,
      "text": "It's over there, behind the teapot.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "在那边，茶壶后面。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 40.86,
      "end": 42.22,
      "text": "Can you see it?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你看得见吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 43.46,
      "end": 49.02,
      "text": "I can see the teapot, but I can't see the tea.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我看得见茶壶，可看不见茶叶。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 49.74,
      "end": 50.9,
      "text": "There it is.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "就在那里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 51.4,
      "end": 52.92,
      "text": "It's in front of you.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "就在你面前。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 53.64,
      "end": 54.74,
      "text": "Ah, yes.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "啊，是的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 55.54,
      "end": 57.36,
      "text": "I can see it now.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我现在看见了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 58.24,
      "end": 60.14,
      "text": "Where are the cups?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "茶杯在哪里？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 61.18,
      "end": 63.36,
      "text": "There are some in the cupboard.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "碗橱里有几只。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 64.18,
      "end": 65.5,
      "text": "Can you find them?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你能找到吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 66.3,
      "end": 68.34,
      "text": "Yes, here they are.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "能，在这里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 69.36,
      "end": 70.32,
      "text": "Hurry up, Sam.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "快点，萨姆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 71.14,
      "end": 72.4,
      "text": "The kettle's boiling.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "水开了。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
